Helm Resources Inc said that, pursuantto the exercise of an overallotment option by underwriters inBamberger Polymers INc's initial public offering, it has soldanother 35,000 Bamberger shares and reduced its ownership inBamberger to 51 pct from 55 pct.    To date, Helm has sold 435,000 Bamberger's for 3.5 mlndlrs.    Bamberger has sold a total of 600,000 shares and receivednet proceeds of about 4.8 mln dlrs since the February 1987offering. Reuter&#3;